name: Om Traders
overview:
Established in the year 2011, at New Delhi (India), we, “Om Traders”, are known as the foremost and reputed wholesaler, supplier and trader of an ample collection of Die Springs, Ball Cage and Plungers, Shoulder Screw, Gas Springs, PU Rod and PU Bush and Ejector Pin and Punch.

Our Products: Our offered range includes Die Springs Round Wire, Spring Ball Plungers, Ground Spacer Sleeve Shoulder Screws, Hexagon Socket Head Shoulder Screw, Nitrogen Gas Springs, Polyurethane Rod and Polyurethane Bush, etc.

Client Satisfaction: Being a customer-focused firm, we channelize all our efforts for their benefit. All our business operations are executed with perfection so as to attain maximum customer satisfaction.

Our Quality: Being a quality oriented organization, highly focused in providing our precious customers the best quality products. In addition to this, we have a team of quality controllers, who keeps an eye on the entire production process to ensure that we are providing our customers optimum quality-centric products.

Our Team: Our experienced professionals make their sincere efforts that assist us in making a good reputation in the market in offering superior quality products to our precious clients.

Vendor Base: We are engaged with certified vendors of the market in order to offer premium quality product range to our clients. In addition to this, we select our vendors with the assistance of our procurement agents who make in-depth market research.
